                ref="#misc_455"
                type="miscellaneous">
               <term xml:id="tag34">
          Timaus the Locrian
        </term>
            </rs> was<lb/>
the first Philosopher of the sect who supported<lb/>
the sublime and sacred doctrine of a<lb/>
primary Creator -<lb/>
One of his treatises is at present in existance<lb/>
It is entitled the soul of the universe<lb/>
            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                n="20"
                xml:id="pb-20"
                facs="#i20"/>
            <lb/>
