               <term xml:id="tag36">
          Timeus
        </term>
            </rs> is said to have taught Philosophy<lb/>
in the middle of the fifth century before<lb/>
the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
