                rend="underline">zealous <rs xml:id="ttag38" ref="#person_445" type="person">
                  <name xml:id="tag38" type="person">
          Pythagorean
        </name>
               </rs>
            </hi>. some fragments<lb/>
of a poem of <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
